content: jkbrooks: Provided significant review contributions with 28 PR approvals while maintaining a sporadic activity pattern across 3 days this month. Opened one PR (#1051) to revert a previous change and created two now-closed issues (#305 and #764) related to the Eliza ecosystem and trading system refactoring.
